title: Cheeseburger Summer Roll
directions: Saut√© onions in olive oil. Add beef and cook through.
Add spinach, relish, salt, and pepper.
NOTE: Add spinach liberally because it will wilt.
When cooked through, allow to cool slightly.
Fill a pot with warm water. Submerge your spring roll wrapper into the water.
Remove wrapper from water and place on a flat, dry surface. Layer on in your filling ingredients.
Fold in the ends of your wrapper, then roll it up snugly.
Roll in sesame coating, serve with mustard and ketchup dip, and enjoy!
